snippet.textDisplay: I'm so glad your back ! I know he won't read this. He doesn't even need to read the comments . Because I'm sure there are negative ones and I want him to keep making videos ! But to put positivity out there ! I had a lumbar puncture done awhile ago and it never healed it kept leaking even with a blood patch.  So now I'm severely sick and can't do anything ! I'm in bed laid down completely flat 247 literally in so much  pain screaming all day and i was hallucinating loosing my mind no matter how much diladid i was on. And I had gotten the lumbar to find out why I was sick already cause I was in bed already for ten years but not this sick ! So wow.. I wish I would have never gotten this done but I say this because I found his videos right when this happened and his videos are the only thing that are making me laugh right now ! 🙂🙂 I'm staying up all night watching them ! Cause I can't even watch my two 6 years olds anymore . So I literally have lost almost everything . So thank you so much for making me and everyone else smile ! I know there are others in way worse situations ! And you made them smile too ! But don't work to hard ! We all want you happy !
